title: Ep. 164 - The Left Applauds The Sexual Exploitation Of A Child
description:
A New York Times editorial argues that the planet would be better off without the human race. On a not entirely unrelated note, an eleven-year-old boy danced in drag at a gay club. The Left, of course, applauds. Date: 12-18-2018
